name: Graphic Design Dublin
blurb:
![Graphic Design Dublin](http://i.minus.com/iqqPQgCN9cPT3.png)

**Graphic Design Dublin** was created for designers interested in networking, collaboration and socialising. Anyone interested in meeting up with other designers; freelancers, employed, unemployed, students or retirees, or are involved in design and would like to share news, info, go to talks etc... as well as learn from each other, feel free to join us.

Follow us on Twitter [https://twitter.com/GraphicDD](@GraphicDD) or connect with us through our Facebook page: [facebook.com/GraphicDesignDublin](https://www.facebook.com/GraphicDesignDublin)

You can also join our group on meetup at [http://www.meetup.com/Graphic-Design-Dublin](http://www.meetup.com/Graphic-Design-Dublin).
